Four people have died on the spot during an accident at Sigana area before reaching Ngiya in Siaya county. Siaya OCPD Ben Chris said the accident was between a motorbike and a bus which was heading to Kisumu from Siaya. Chris said the two vehicles suffered a head on coalition and the four people who were riding a motorbike died on the spot. Nobody from the bus was injured. The vehicle was towed to Siaya Police station.